data.description: **SELLER OFFERING $10,000 CREDIT FOR BUYERS CLOSING COSTS/RATE BUYDOWN**Welcome to your new home! This 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom house features granite countertops in the kitchen, hardwood and tile floors on the main level, and crown molding for added charm. Enjoy a hot tub in the fenced backyard or relax on the covered front porch. In addition to the main level, the basement offers a finished room for extra space, and there's also a semi-finished room of approximately 300 sq. ft.  That's almost 1800 sqft heated and cooled!  Conveniently located, this house is ready to become your forever home. Alpha, West View, and West High Schools. Don't miss out, schedule a viewing today!
